targets.rawQuery:
with ds as (
SELECT tag, CREATE_TIME_SERIES(time, measure_value::double) as _ 
FROM $__database.$__table 
where $__timeFilter
group by tag )
select tag, _  from ds

SELECT * FROM $__database.$__table where $__timeFilter 
and tag = '$Tags' LIMIT 10

SELECT tag, 
max(measure_value::double) as max_value, 
min(measure_value::double) as min_value,
avg(measure_value::double) as avg_value,
stddev(measure_value::double) as std
FROM $__database.$__table group  by tag

SELECT  time, measure_value::double FROM $__database.$__table where tag = '$Tags'
and $__timeFilter
